**North Warehousing** is a vertically integrated platform that provides **warehouse storage**, **multi-vendor management**, and **real-time logistics solutions** to importers, exporters, and domestic businesses in Ghana. 

Our goal is to provide **intelligent storage matching**, **integrated truck/parcel movement**, and a seamless frontend experience for **warehouse owners**, **logistics partners**, **storefront vendors**, and **end customers** â€” all through a secure, modular web system.

